node.text:
Making delicious “Pineapple Angel” cocktail with @lobos1707 and @chilledmagazine 
⠀
🍸
How to:
🍸
Cut fresh pineapple
Take a shaker and put 50g of fresh pineapple
Add 1/4 oz of sugar syrup
Muddle it
Squeeze fresh lime juice 3/4 oz
Add 4 sage leaves
Add 1 1/2 oz of @lobos1707 tequila
Add 3/4 oz of peach liqueur
 Add plenty of ice
Shake all ingredients
Fine strain into a chilled coupe glass
Garnish with sage
Enjoy!
🥃
Tag us in your story if you made it and have a wonderful day!
⠀
#allforthepack #chilled100 #nextlevelbartending
⠀

#CocktailsAtHome

🥥
🥑

You will need shaker
Squeeze fresh lime juice
Add agave nectar
Add avocado 🥑
Muddle it
Add coconut 🥥 yogurt
Add tequila
Add plenty of ice
Shake everything
Pour into chilled glass with ice
